ActIndian Act
SubjectAddition to Kahnawake Indian Reserve No. 14, in Quebec
PrecisOrder setting apart 90.98 hectares (224.82 acres) of lands, excluding mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Mohawks of Kahnawà:ke Band as an addition to KAHNAWAKE INDIAN RESERVE NO. 14, located in the registration divisions of Châteauguay - Lacolle and Laprairie, in the municipality of Saint-Constant and the municipality of Saint-Isidore, Quebec.
